5. Adversarial Training: Models hardened against adversarial examples
6. Model Access Logs: All inference calls logged and monitored
7. A/B Testing: Monitoring for model drift and performance degradation

ACCEPTANCE PERIOD: 45 days (TensorFlow upgrade during next sprint)
