───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

AWS Security Team,

We acknowledge the 30-day runtime update timeline for CVE-2024-9204.

DECISION: Accept risk until June 5 runtime update

RATIONALE:
1. Serverless architecture provides strong isolation guarantees
2. WAF + input validation block exploit vectors
3. 30-day window is minimal (shorter than typical patch cycles)
4. Automatic runtime update requires zero engineering effort

We will enable automatic runtime updates on June 5 when Python 3.11
patch is released.

DevOps Team

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
END OF EMAIL CORRESPONDENCE
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════`,

